OpenBSD 7.8 errata 038, June 2, 2026:

Fixes for a variety of crashing bugs in smtpd(8).

Apply by doing:
    signify -Vep /etc/signify/openbsd-78-base.pub -x 038_smtpd.patch.sig \
        -m - | (cd /usr/src && patch -p0)

And then rebuild and install smtpd and smtpctl:
    cd /usr/src/usr.sbin/smtpd
    make obj
    make
    make install

